Sentence.value: The protein urine dipstick test measures the presence of proteins, such as albumin, in a urine sample.
Sentence.pattern_crowdsource: The protein urine dipstick test measures the presence of [[proteins|C0033684]], such as [[albumin|C0001924]], in a urine sample.

Sentence.value: The health care provider uses a dipstick made with a color-sensitive pad.
Sentence.pattern_crowdsource: The [[health care provider|C0018724]] uses a dipstick made with a color-sensitive [[pad|C0182158]].

Sentence.value: The following may also interfere with test results: - Dehydration - Dye (contrast media) if you have a radiology scan within 3 days before the urine test - Strenuous exercise - Urinary tract infection - Urine contaminated with fluids from the vagina
Sentence.pattern_crowdsource: The following may also interfere with test results: - Dehydration - Dye (contrast media) if you have a radiology [[scan|C0441633]] within 3 days before the urine test - Strenuous exercise - Urinary tract infection - Urine contaminated with fluids from the [[vagina|C0042232]]
